---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Keep Aligned" description="Privacy Policy for Keep Aligned - Your orthodontic treatment tracking app.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
          Keep Aligned ‚Äî Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-500">
          Last updated: December 25, 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">
          
          <p class="text-neutral-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Thank you for using Keep Aligned ("the App"), developed by Agust√≠n Arone Castellari.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed italic">
            If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, please do not access the App.
          </p>

          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</span>
              Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              We collect only the data strictly necessary for the App's functionality. Keep Aligned does not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for advertising or marketing purposes.
            </p>

            <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">1.1 Personal Data (Provided by You)</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Profile information (name, email, or other optional identifiers).</li>
                  <li>Aligner tracking data you manually enter (e.g., aligner number, usage logs).</li>
                  <li>Optional health-related notes you choose to record in the App.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">1.2 Automatically Collected Data</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Basic device information (model, OS version, system language).</li>
                  <li>Usage analytics (anonymous and aggregated) to improve stability and performance.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-success-50 border border-success-100 rounded-xl p-4">
                <p class="text-success-600 font-medium mb-2">We do not collect:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Precise location data</li>
                  <li>Contact lists</li>
                  <li>Payment information (the App does not process payments)</li>
                  <li>Sensitive personal identifiers (ID, passport, etc.)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">We use the information collected to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-1 ml-4">
              <li>Operate and maintain the App</li>
              <li>Store your aligner progress and usage history</li>
              <li>Improve user experience and app performance</li>
              <li>Provide customer support if needed</li>
              <li>Detect and fix bugs or technical issues</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              Data Storage and Security
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              Your data is securely stored using modern cloud infrastructure with industry-standard encryption.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no digital platform is fully secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              If future versions allow syncing your account across devices, we will implement additional authentication and encryption layers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              Sharing of Information
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              We do not share any personal data with third parties except in the following cases:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> trusted vendors who help us operate the App (e.g., hosting, analytics). They process data solely on our behalf.</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> if required to comply with applicable laws, court orders, or legal processes.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
              We do not share your data with advertisers or use it for targeted advertising.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 5 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">5</span>
              Children's Privacy
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              Keep Aligned is not intended for children under 13.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that personal data from a child under 13 has been collected, we will delete it promptly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 6 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">6</span>
              Your Rights and Choices
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Depending on your region, you may have rights to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-1 ml-4">
              <li>Access your stored data</li>
              <li>Correct or update your information</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
              <li>Request a copy of your data (data portability)</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="bg-brand-50 border border-brand-100 rounded-xl p-4 mt-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-700">To exercise these rights, contact us at:</p>
              <a href="mailto:agustinarone@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
                <span>üì©</span> agustinarone@gmail.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 7 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">7</span>
              Third-Party Links and External Services
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              The App may include links to external websites or support documents. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those external sites.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 8 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">8</span>
              International Data Transfers
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              Your data may be processed and stored in servers located outside your country of residence.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              By using the App, you consent to this transfer under applicable data protection regulations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 9 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">9</span>
              Policy Updates
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              When we do, we will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. Significant changes will be communicated within the App when required.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 10 -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">10</span>
              Contact Us
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
              If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the handling of your data, please contact:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-lg mb-3">Agust√≠n Arone Castellari</p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <a href="mailto:agustinarone@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span>üìß</span> agustinarone@gmail.com
                </a>
                <a href="https://agusarone.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span>üåê</span> agusarone.com
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Back link -->
          <div class="pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium transition-colors group">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
              </svg>
              Volver al inicio
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

